  <mainDescription>&lt;a id=&quot;Top&quot; name=&quot;Top&quot;>&lt;/a> &#xD;
&lt;h3>&#xD;
    Overview&amp;nbsp;&#xD;
&lt;/h3>&#xD;
&lt;p>&#xD;
    This tool mentor supports performing Describe Distribution with Rational XDE Developer - Java Platform Edition.&#xD;
&lt;/p>&#xD;
&lt;ul>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        The steps in this tool mentor match those in the corresponding task.&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        Links to topics in XDE online Help are marked with &lt;img alt=&quot;helpbook icon&quot; src=&quot;../../resources/helpbook.gif&quot; />.&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        The following steps are performed in this tool mentor:&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
    &lt;li style=&quot;LIST-STYLE-TYPE: none&quot;>&#xD;
        &lt;ul>&#xD;
            &lt;li>&#xD;
                &lt;a href=&quot;#Analyze%20Distribution%20Requirements&quot;>Analyze Distribution Requirements&lt;/a>&#xD;
            &lt;/li>&#xD;
            &lt;li>&#xD;
                &lt;a href=&quot;#Define%20the%20Network%20Configuration&quot;>Define the Network Configuration&lt;/a>&#xD;
            &lt;/li>&#xD;
            &lt;li>&#xD;
                &lt;a href=&quot;#Allocate%20System%20Elements%20to%20Nodes&quot;>Allocate System Elements to Nodes&lt;/a> &amp;nbsp;&#xD;
            &lt;/li>&#xD;
        &lt;/ul>&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
&lt;/ul>&#xD;
&lt;h3>&#xD;
    &lt;a id=&quot;Analyze Distribution Requirements&quot; name=&quot;Analyze Distribution Requirements&quot;>Analyze Distribution&#xD;
    Requirements&lt;/a>&#xD;
&lt;/h3>&#xD;
&lt;p>&#xD;
    There is no Rational XDE (TM) specific guidance for this step.&#xD;
&lt;/p>&#xD;
&lt;h3>&#xD;
    &lt;a id=&quot;Define the Network Configuration&quot; name=&quot;Define the Network Configuration&quot;>Define the Network Configuration&lt;/a>&#xD;
&lt;/h3>&#xD;
&lt;p>&#xD;
    Refine the deployment diagram created in &lt;a class=&quot;elementLinkWithType&quot;&#xD;
    href=&quot;./../../../core.base_rup/tasks/architectural_analysis_2B9BE03.html&quot; guid=&quot;{8CB48402-D4C5-4E17-BB33-507315CB1BBF}&quot;>Task:&#xD;
    Architectural Analysis&lt;/a> (&lt;a class=&quot;elementLinkWithUserText&quot;&#xD;
    href=&quot;./../../../core.base_rup/guidances/toolmentors/performing_architectural_analysis_65CE30FC.html&quot;&#xD;
    guid=&quot;{08B5477D-97F9-4EEB-AA59-A109128B5CA1}&quot;>Tool Mentor: Performing Architectural Analysis Using Rational XDE&lt;/a>).&#xD;
&lt;/p>&#xD;
&lt;p>&#xD;
    Reference: &lt;img alt=&quot;helpbook icon&quot; src=&quot;../../resources/helpbook.gif&quot; /> &lt;i>Working with Deployment Diagrams&lt;/i> &#xD;
    &lt;!--//ReferenceHelpTopic(topicTitle,&quot;rs&quot;,&quot;rs_o_work_with_deploy_dgm&quot;);                  -->&#xD;
&lt;/p>&#xD;
&lt;h3>&#xD;
    &lt;a id=&quot;Allocate System Elements to Nodes&quot; name=&quot;Allocate System Elements to Nodes&quot;>Allocate System Elements to&#xD;
    Nodes&lt;/a>&#xD;
&lt;/h3>&#xD;
&lt;p>&#xD;
    Annotate the deployment diagram, or add additional diagrams, to show logical deployment (classes, subsystems, or&#xD;
    threads of control mapped to nodes), and/or physical deployment (files or sets of files mapped to nodes). The steps are&#xD;
    as follows:&#xD;
&lt;/p>&#xD;
&lt;ol>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        Add additional deployment diagrams as needed. Reference: &lt;img alt=&quot;helpbook icon&quot;&#xD;
        src=&quot;../../resources/helpbook.gif&quot; /> &lt;i>Adding Diagrams&lt;/i> &#xD;
        &lt;!--//ReferenceHelpTopic(topicTitle,&quot;rs&quot;,&quot;rs_t_add_dgm&quot;);                  -->&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        Add nodes or node instances to the diagram. Reference: &lt;img alt=&quot;helpbook icon&quot;&#xD;
        src=&quot;../../resources/helpbook.gif&quot; /> &lt;i>Adding Shapes to Diagrams&lt;/i> &#xD;
        &lt;!--//ReferenceHelpTopic(topicTitle,&quot;rs&quot;,&quot;rs_t_add_shp_dgm&quot;);                  -->&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        Drag and drop design model elements or implementation model elements onto the diagram. Reference: &lt;img&#xD;
        alt=&quot;helpbook icon&quot; src=&quot;../../resources/helpbook.gif&quot; /> &lt;i>Adding Shapes to Diagrams&lt;/i> &#xD;
        &lt;!--//ReferenceHelpTopic(topicTitle,&quot;rs&quot;,&quot;rs_t_add_shp_dgm&quot;);                  -->If the element to be deployed is&#xD;
        not yet modeled, add it as needed to the appropriate model. (See &lt;a class=&quot;elementLinkWithUserText&quot;&#xD;
        href=&quot;./../../../core.base_rup/guidances/whitepapers/model_structure_guidelines_for_rational_xde_developer_6D2FD64A.html&quot;&#xD;
        guid=&quot;2.67081400527339E-306&quot;>Rational XDE Model Structure Guidelines&lt;/a> for where each kind of element is&#xD;
        modeled.)&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        Add deploy relationships between nodes and deployed elements. Reference: &lt;img alt=&quot;helpbook icon&quot;&#xD;
        src=&quot;../../resources/helpbook.gif&quot; /> &lt;i>Adding Deploy Relationships&lt;/i> &#xD;
        &lt;!--//ReferenceHelpTopic(topicTitle,&quot;rs&quot;,&quot;rs_t_adding_deploy_rels&quot;);                  -->&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
&lt;/ol>&#xD;
&lt;p>&#xD;
    Reference: &lt;img alt=&quot;helpbook icon&quot; src=&quot;../../resources/helpbook.gif&quot; /> &lt;i>Working with Deployment Diagrams&lt;/i> &#xD;
    &lt;!--//ReferenceHelpTopic(topicTitle,&quot;rs&quot;,&quot;rs_o_work_with_deploy_dgm&quot;);                  -->&#xD;
&lt;/p>&#xD;
&lt;p>&#xD;
    &lt;br />&#xD;
    &lt;br />&#xD;
&lt;/p></mainDescription>
